title: Raised Garden Bed, Galvanized Raised Garden Beds Outdoor for Vegetables Flowers Herbs, Steel Large Deep Root Planter Box, Tall Raised Garden Bed Kit with 1Pc Gloves and Metal Fix Stake, Black 6×3×2FT
feature_bullets: ✔ Large Raised Garden Bed: 2FT tall planter box provides more space to deep root vegetables, herbs, flowers and plants.
✔ Galvanized Raised Garden Bed: Steel garden kit made of stable thickened galvanized metal. Metal garden bed is anti-rust, durable,sturdy and long-lasting frame.
✔ Open-Bottom Garden Frame: Metal raised garden bed kit protects plant roots. Provides good drainage keeps the soil and nutrients and keeps away from pests and diseases.

✔ Environment-Friendly: Outdoor raised garden beds has eco-friendly coating do not contaminate soil,safe for plants and humans. Each board has plastic film to protect the paint and prevent scratches. Plastic protective film can be torn off before installation. Please do not mistake the lines of plastic film for scratches.

✔ Best assembled by two people at the same time: Due to the high height of this raised bed, it will be a little difficulty for one person to assemble. Large patio bed kit is easy to put together by two people, only a few minutes. Hardware assembly manual and gloves are included.
